snippet.title: Shardfall: FitQuest VR | Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing Shardfall: FitQuest VR, now available to pre-order on the Meta Store. 

Shardfall: FitQuest VR launches on 7 January 2025! 

Burn more than 600 kcals per hour with high-intensity, full-body workouts, while enjoying an immersive fitness gaming experience. 

Pre-order now on the Meta Store: https://www.meta.com/en-gb/experiences/shardfall-fitquest-vr/9063040383758002/
Find out more via playquell.com
